WEBVTT

00:00.003 --> 00:01.190
<i>Previously on "The Bold Type"...</i>

00:01.289 --> 00:02.680
Running's actually fun, you know?

00:02.723 --> 00:03.971
Once you get into the spirit of it.

00:03.992 --> 00:06.036
Yeah, me... I'm more of a sitting girl.

00:06.126 --> 00:08.025
Like on a bench.

00:08.061 --> 00:09.527
- Pamela Dolan.
- The photographer?

00:09.563 --> 00:11.996
I think she's been abusing her models.

00:12.031 --> 00:13.965
My arms got so tired I fell.

00:14.000 --> 00:15.367
If Pamela finds out I talked to you,

00:15.402 --> 00:17.001
she will ruin my career.

00:17.036 --> 00:19.170
I'm down to the last few names.

00:19.205 --> 00:21.106
- No one's willing to back up her story?
- No.

00:21.204 --> 00:24.342
Tia was working on this
campaign for City Council.

00:24.377 --> 00:27.378
- I went in to volunteer...
- And left as the candidate.

00:27.413 --> 00:29.280
One minute she's acting
like she's my date.

00:29.315 --> 00:30.647
<i>And then the next minute,</i>

00:30.683 --> 00:32.283
it's all endorsements and ad buys.

00:32.317 --> 00:33.784
The first time I kissed a girl

00:33.819 --> 00:35.819
it was terrifying,
'cause I knew this was

00:35.855 --> 00:39.423
<i>what I wanted,
and I don't wanna want it.</i>

00:40.659 --> 00:43.928
I'm obsessed with
harlequin romance novels

00:43.963 --> 00:46.163
and renaissance fairs.

00:46.199 --> 00:49.000
I have the most insane
collection of Snuggies,

00:49.035 --> 00:51.269
and I'm the best snuggler.

00:51.304 --> 00:52.904
My dream is to be an opera singer,

00:52.939 --> 00:54.939
so I practice a lot.

00:54.974 --> 00:56.440
A lot.

00:56.475 --> 00:58.276
So, then I told my parents,

00:58.311 --> 00:59.843
you shouldn't have called me Madeline

00:59.879 --> 01:01.612
if you don't even like the name Maddy.

01:02.748 --> 01:04.581
Makes sense.

01:04.617 --> 01:06.482
Do all three of you live here?

01:06.518 --> 01:08.051
Oh, God no.

01:08.954 --> 01:10.053
I used to.

01:10.088 --> 01:11.221
Their opinions matter.

01:11.256 --> 01:12.588
Greatly.

01:12.624 --> 01:14.024
You know what?

01:14.059 --> 01:15.425
I'm good.

01:15.460 --> 01:16.893
What does that mean, you're good?

01:16.929 --> 01:19.963
I just don't think this is gonna work.

01:19.998 --> 01:22.899
Are you... rejecting us?

01:22.935 --> 01:24.401
No, she's rejecting me.

01:24.436 --> 01:25.468
I'm the one who needs a roommate.

01:25.503 --> 01:26.736
No one's rejecting Jane.

01:26.771 --> 01:28.771
I'll see myself out.

01:30.242 --> 01:31.707
That's okay, we'll see you out.

01:31.743 --> 01:32.875
Yeah.

01:36.748 --> 01:38.415
Thank you so much for your time.

01:38.450 --> 01:40.283
We'll let you know what we decide.

01:40.319 --> 01:41.651
You're all insane.

